Application converts whole websites to ebook.

BLOG
-It gets an url of a blog home page
-Crawl and parse it to get every single uniq url within a url 
-Parse every single subpage to get a title, date, content with pics and create object from page
  check if html, fix imgs to absolute path, 
- check if it is article or just list of articles(for duplicate content in page. delete page which has more duplicates. If it has only one leave both) 
- remove repeating content (probably some fb and others stuff)
- Sort objects by date
- create one html doc
- save the doc as a ebook

IDEAS:
- create a cover based on keywords and screen of website
- create table of contents basen on titles of chapters
- parse also paginating

